Package: rust-toolchain-1.86
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, gcc, libc6-dev
Provides: rust-compiler
Description: Rust 1.86.0 toolchain for arm64 (binary repackage)
 Official Rust 1.86.0 compiler toolchain repackaged as a .deb for
 arm64/aarch64. Installs to /usr/lib/rust-1.86/ and provides rustc,
 cargo, and the standard library. Does not conflict with system rustc.
